{"id":"gotcha-mini-001","type":"gotcha","fact":"A test fake that re-declares the plugin context shape can silently drift from the real createContext and hide a runtime crash. The removed bb plugin destructured { DEVEL_ROOT } (uppercase) while the context exposes develRoot (lowercase); its test used the same wrong key, so 'mini bb local' crashed in production while the suite stayed green.","recommendation":"Derive createMockContext from the real createContext (spread it; override only http/shell/prompt and a hermetic config.read). Never hand-roll the context shape in a test.","confidence":"high","provenance":[{"source":"agent","reference":"self-assessment rounds 1-2","date":"2026-06-23"}],"tags":["testing","context","drift","plugins"],"affectedFiles":["tests/helpers/mock-context.js","lib/plugin-context.js"],"affectedServices":[],"createdAt":"2026-06-23T00:00:00Z","updatedAt":"2026-06-23T00:00:00Z","usageCount":0,"helpfulCount":0,"outdatedReports":0}
